body_html: I tried a graph traversal using both while_loop with auto JIT option on and simply while under eager mode. It seems eager while runs faster. And my implementation is slower than existing method in sklearn based on cython, although I tried to use matrix manipulation as much as possible to gain efficiency from GPU.
